弗拉特黑德縣是州中毗鄰縣數量最多的縣份。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.princeton.edu/~achaney/tmve/wiki100k/docs/Flathead_County,_Montana.html|title=Flathead County, Montana|publisher=princeton.edu|accessdate=2013-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011355/http://www.princeton.edu/~achaney/tmve/wiki100k/docs/Flathead_County,_Montana.html|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

